::Prowl::

Prowl lowers his gun as Iron Raptor stops moving, looking at her cautioustly. 
Her reaction convinced him that she was Iron Raptor, but he was still 
wondering why she was acting that way.

He takes a step forward, leaving his gun on a table. "Iron Raptor, is that 
you?"
